    # m "I'm a queen of mediocrity."
    m "おもしろくない人の女王なの、私が。"

# game/day2.rpy:1554
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_b670eeaa:

    # m "You won't believe how jealous I am of someone with raw, natural talent."
    m "私が自然な才能を持つ人をどれほど羨ましいと思っているか分からないでしょ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1556
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_da0c156a:

    # m "It's the only way to be number one."
    m "それがナンバーワンになる唯一の方法なの。"

# game/day2.rpy:1558
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_a446cc6b:

    # p "I see where you're going, but raw talent is a waste if not honed."
    p "言っていることが分かるけど、磨かれない才能は無駄だよ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1559
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_f546b65d:

    # p "And talented people are often lazy, so if you work more, you can catch up!"
    p "で、才能のある人はなまけてるから、頑張れば追いかけられる。"

# game/day2.rpy:1561
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_fafceeb0:

    # m "Only if there's enough time."
    m "時間があれば"

# game/day2.rpy:1563
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_a54aa352:

    # m "Sadly, I'm already behind... I hate it, I really do!"
    m "残念だけど、私はもう遅れてる。"

# game/day2.rpy:1565
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_95b75489:

    # p "You're kidding me."
    p "そんなことあるよ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1567
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_729520c2:

    # m "I'm afraid not."
    m "そんなことあるよ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1569
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_95a6be1f:

    # m "Say, if I wanted to go into figure skating..."
    m "例えば、フィギュアスケートは..."

# game/day2.rpy:1571
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_8bfc207a:

    # p "Isn't this a bit of an extreme example?"
    p "少し極端な例じゃないかな。"

# game/day2.rpy:1573
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_75dba3c2:

    # m "Okay, let's talk about drawing. I always wanted to be good at it."
    m "分かった。じゃ、絵を描くのはどうですか。昔から上手くなりたかったの。"

# game/day2.rpy:1575
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_0bbe3afa:

    # m "If I start now, in two years I'll be pretty decent..."
    m "今から始めると、2年後にはかなりまともになると思うし..."

# game/day2.rpy:1577
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_737c3f3d:

    # m "But those who started ten years ago will be presented in art galleries."
    m "でも、10年前に始めた人はアートギャラリーで展示を開くでしょ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1579
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_d0f6e2e0:

    # m "But the punchline is..."
    m "でも結果は…"

# game/day2.rpy:1581
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_c5597036:

    # m "These art galleries would {i}always{/i} be named after someone with raw talent."
    m "アートギャラリーは、{i}いつも{/i} 才能のある人にちなんで命名されてる。"

# game/day2.rpy:1583
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_71e41244:

    # p "Trust me, you still have enough time, Marta!"
    p "僕を信じて！時間はまだたっぷりあるよ、マルタ！"

# game/day2.rpy:1585
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_1511cc76:

    # m "Maybe, but I really need to make up my mind and concentrate on... something."
    m "そうかもしれないけど、私は本当に覚悟を決めて、集中しなきゃいけない...何かに。"

# game/day2.rpy:1587
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_0069a007:

    # m "\"Something\"... Screw it, I have zero idea about what I want to do!"
    m "\「何かに\」…　何がしたいのか、アイディアがまったくないの！"

# game/day2.rpy:1589
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_31c89ee8:

    # p "Well, have you tried discussing it with your parents?"
    p "両親と相談したことある？"

# game/day2.rpy:1591
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_c3135a60:

    # m "I despise them."
    m "私、あの人たちを軽蔑してるの。"

# game/day2.rpy:1593
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_db1f5e1a:

    # p "Why?"
    p "どうして？"

# game/day2.rpy:1595
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_103a07fd:

    # m "My father settled down and tried to drag me along."
    m "私の父親は自分が重しくない人だからって私のことまで面白くない人にさせようとするの。"

# game/day2.rpy:1597
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_53804468:

    # m "I asked countless times to get me into arts, dancing, whatever..."
    m "私は絵画やダンスを習いに行きたいって何回もお願いしたのに..."

# game/day2.rpy:1599
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_49ad74a0:

    # m "You know, just to try it out and see if it's my thing."
    m "ただやってみたかったのに…"

# game/day2.rpy:1601
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_e756c059:

    # m "He always told me I should forget this nonsense and study hard."
    m "そんなばかばかしいことを忘れて、真面目に勉強しろって言われた。"

# game/day2.rpy:1603
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_9dc5cceb:

    # m "To live a decent life, he said..."
    m "普通の生活のためにって…"

# game/day2.rpy:1605
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_1b05d60d:

    # m "And my mother... I don't even know her well. But that's another story."
    m "で、母は…母はあまり知らない、私は。別の話なんだけど。"

# game/day2.rpy:1607
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_38d97d88:

    # p "I don't know what to say..."
    p "そんな…"

# game/day2.rpy:1609
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_acd9e505:

    # m "Well, excuse me for this rant."
    m "こんなに愚痴を言ってごめん。"

# game/day2.rpy:1611
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_3777be7b:

    # m "Actually, thanks for listening. I feel a bit better now!"
    m "聞いてくれて、ありがとう。気分がよくなったよ！"

# game/day2.rpy:1613
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_7d873c52:

    # m "Hey, why are you looking at me like that, [player_name]?"
    m "どうしてそんなに見つめるの、[player_name]？"

# game/day2.rpy:1615
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_4c64c484:

    # m "Don't think I opened up or anything."
    m "心を開いたとか思わないでね。"

# game/day2.rpy:1617
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_e2d59fe4:

    # p "I just go over what you said, Marta."
    p "マルタが言ってたことについて考えてただけだよ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1619
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_f7f2af80:

    # m "Really? Well then, take your time!"
    m "本当？じゃあ、ごゆっくり！"

# game/day2.rpy:1621
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_5e93503a:

    # m "You're walking painfully slow anyway."
    m "死ぬほどゆっくり歩っているんだよ。"

# game/day2.rpy:1623
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_09fbe708:

    # m "See you tomorrow!"
    m "また明日！"

# game/day2.rpy:1625
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_830a0976:

    # m "I... I'll be glad to see you tomorrow..."
    m "あ-あしたを楽しみにしてる。"

# game/day2.rpy:1635
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_2bae8c3f:

    # "We're about to get going."
    "私たちは出発しようとしてる"

# game/day2.rpy:1636
translate japanese day2_road_home_marta_4135a80f:

    # "In fact, Teya already left us."
    "実のところ、テヤはもう先に行ってた"

# game/day2.rpy:1637
